Other Laboratories
* Biosphere 2 – designed as an artificially closed complete ecology, and was the setting for research on human interaction with natural systems. The site is now owned and maintained by the University of Arizona, which conducts tours for the public. Beware that the scientific credentials of the initial project phase is quite unclear as it started as theatre group. For example no input was taken from the Antarctic research stations, where researcher experience extreme confinement.
